43 Sanidassanattika, Saṃkiliṭṭhattika
Sanidassanattika, Saṃkiliṭṭhattika
52.
165Nasanidassanasappaṭighaṃ nasaṃkiliṭṭhasaṃkilesikaṃ dhammaṃ paccayā anidassanaappaṭigho saṃkiliṭṭhasaṃkilesiko dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (Saṃkhittaṃ.) Hetuyā tīṇi…pe…  avigate tīṇi.
166Nasanidassanasappaṭighaṃ naasaṃkiliṭṭhasaṃkilesikaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca sanidassanasappaṭigho asaṃkiliṭṭhasaṃkilesiko dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (Saṃkhittaṃ.) Hetuyā ekavīsa, adhipatiyā ekavīsa…pe…  avigate ekavīsa.
